title: AoK goes to KIFF!
contentMarkdown:
A wonderful news! AoK will officially premiere at the 31st Kolkata International Film Festival, to be held from 6-13 November. 

It will play as part of the National Competition of Short Films. Screening times and venues to be shared soon.

For me, this is a dream come true. KIFF was the only Film Festival I had ever attended before I started making films myself. I remember attending numerous screenings, with the lingering question in my mind- Would I ever get to see my own film up there? Today that question has an answer.

See you at the screening!
SD
Oct 25'
